thread.title: Valerie

author: Valerie
title: Valerie
text: I purchased a new choral music folder for myself after years of using black 3-ring binders that would wear out or crack from much use. The folder I received is high quality with all of the pockets, tabs I could want plus the ability to store music with elastic stays and 3-ring options. I expect this folder to last me for a very long time because of its quality construction. Thank you.
